text:
New rock has a line of sustainable and vegan shoes.

&amp;#x200B;

Edit to clarify: not all of the new rock shoes are vegan leather. many of them are actually made from scraps of fabric.

Hello, I work at Compare Ethics - the global ethical comparison website. We feature over 30 verified ethical brands! [www.compareethics.com](https://www.compareethics.com) :) 

&amp;#x200B;

We also have a blog on common practices: [https://compareethics.com/blog/](https://compareethics.com/blog/)

&amp;#x200B;

Abbie
